<div id="empty_slate_system_roles" class="empty_slate">
  <h3>{lang}About Task Segments{/lang}</h3>

  <ul class="icon_list">
    <li>
      <img src="{image_url name="empty-slates/segments.png" module=$smarty.const.TASKS_MODULE}" class="icon_list_icon" alt="" />
      <span class="icon_list_title">{lang}What are Task Segments?{/lang}</span>
      <span class="icon_list_description">{lang}Task segments let you filter tasks that match specified criteria. For example, you can define segment "Defects" that lists all tasks that are in "Bug Reports" category and have CONFIRMED or FIXED label{/lang}.</span>
    </li>

    <li>
      <img src="{image_url name="empty-slates/help.png" module=$smarty.const.ENVIRONMENT_FRAMEWORK}" class="icon_list_icon" alt="" />
      <span class="icon_list_title">{lang}Reuse Segments in Other Reports{/lang}</span>
      <span class="icon_list_description">{lang}Once you define a task segment, you can use it in other reports in Reports and Filters section. For example, you can use your "Defects" segment in Weekly Completed Tasks report to see how fast your team is going through reported defects{/lang}.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>